      "name": "K9 - #66b Lantern",
      "effect": "If your opponent has 2 or more cards in their hand, you can Normal Summon this card without Tributing. You can only use each of the following effects of \"K9 - #66b Lantern\" once per turn. If this card is in your hand: You can target 1 non-Pyro Level 5 \"K9\" monster in your GY; Special Summon both it and this card, but they cannot be used as material for the Xyz Summon of a LIGHT monster. During your Main Phase: You can add 1 \"K9\" Spell/Trap from your Deck to your hand.",
      "official": false
